Big Joe Portagee is Large, slow witted, lazy, and weak willed, Big Joe is something of an anti-hero inTortilla Flatyet he still manages to garner some sympathy from readers. He has to be pushed to do good things, but once he gets going, he is a force to be reckoned with. He often does bad things by accident, not really meaning harm, but just forgetting what he is supposed to do.